### Upload a document (replace {{TOKEN}} with JWT and adjust multipart)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/documents/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=BOUNDARY

--BOUNDARY
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Sample text content
--BOUNDARY--

### List documents with pagination
GET http://localhost:4000/api/documents?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/api/documents/{{DOCUMENT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Analyze
POST http://localhost:4000/api/documents/{{DOCUMENT_ID}}/analyze
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update metadata
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/documents/{{DOCUMENT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documentType": "contract",
  "tags": ["shareholders", "board"],
  "metadata": {
    "jurisdiction": "India"
  }
}

### Download
GET http://localhost:4000/api/documents/{{DOCUMENT_ID}}/download
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Delete
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/documents/{{DOCUMENT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
